Test/DBunit version 0.04
===========================
    Simple database test interface.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Abstract::Meta::Class 
  DBIx::Connection
  Simple::SAX::Serializer
  Test::Pod
  Test::Pod::Coverage

